items.title: Democratic Rep. Gerry Connolly dies at 75
items.description: Democratic Rep. Gerry Connolly of Virginia has died, his office announced Wednesday morning. He was 75 years old.

items.title: WATCH:  Driver trapped after dump truck slams into home
items.description: Emergency crews rushed to a chaotic scene Tuesday afternoon after a dump truck plowed into a home in New Jersey.

items.title: House GOP works to push through bill advancing Trump's agenda
items.description: House Republicans have worked through the night to move a megabill advancing President Donald Trump's legislative agenda through a key committee.

items.title: Trump admin live updates: Freedom Caucus chair says 'no way' budget bill passes today
items.description: Freedom Caucus Chairman Andy Harris said there is “no way” the “One Big Beautiful Bill Act” passes in the House on Wednesday.

items.title: Target CEO says tariffs risk 'massive' costs, but price hikes a 'last resort'
items.description: Target reported a drop in sales in its most recent quarter.
